def is_food_chicken_cuttable(chicken:item):
    symbol chicken_cuttable = is_food_chicken(chicken) and cuttable(chicken)

behavior slice_chicken(chicken:item, knife:item, cutting_board:item):
    body:
        achieve on(chicken, cutting_board)
        # Ensure the chicken is on the cutting board for slicing

        achieve close(knife, chicken)
        # Bring the knife close to the chicken 

        achieve cut(chicken)
        # Cut the chicken
